{"tid":1662423,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[BACKUP] 死魚姐，又唔係死人，東方日報咁都要維隱？？？？？？","createTime":"2019-10-18T18:01:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T18:04:49.000Z","uid":232845,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"aee26425f5baa2445117e75d76c73fa5a35827c0","tid":1662423,"uid":232845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T18:01:27.000Z","msg":"昨晚(18日)11時左右，有市民路經觀塘碼頭海旁，發現對開海面，漂浮着大量死魚，據現場目測接近1千條，平均每條體形大約1隻手掌大小，沿着碼頭邊緣綿延數百米，一直延伸至貨物起卸區，場面駭人。<br />\n有目擊者當場被面前景象嚇倒，驚魂甫定後由其他在場人士提醒：「喂，999先啦呢度！」未知最終是否有警員到場處理。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">東網記者及後到達現場了解，但見海面一切如常，未有發現死魚漂浮。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191019/bkn-20191019000359113-1019_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191019%2Fbkn-20191019000359113-1019_00822_001.html&d=hAhx4mZ6jCiP%2Fv5W8BSz9jKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=30f4c9c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191019/bkn-20191019000359113-1019_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BE8PSJa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBE8PSJa.png&h=4713240b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c83e7ac2c34309f068fe8c6453d26a20923d0ed1","tid":1662423,"uid":301814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T18:02:35.000Z","msg":"唔比人拎啲魚去驗..."},{"pid":"b14c5029a7ed64ca8ac137825574549c8d2fcfed","tid":1662423,"uid":232845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T18:02:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dae9bcc1c0afd14ec48949027335320f8e422d38","tid":1662423,"uid":301814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T18:03:47.000Z","msg":"冇魚驗就拎海水驗啦 唔係咁都要人教呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src